memberdef.argsstring: (const SG::AuxVectorData *in, IThinningSvc *svc, const IThinningSvc::Filter_t &filter, const IThinningSvc::Operator::Type op)
memberdef.name: thinningHook

briefdescription.para: Propagate thinning. Called after applying thinning to in.

detaileddescription.para:
in
The object that was thinned.
svc
The thinning service (for convenience).
filter
Lists the elements to be kept.
op
How to merge results: AND or OR.
This will be called whenever a request is made to thin a DataVector.
Otherwise, we pass the thinning request on to the aux store, provided that it exists and is in the event store.

briefdescription.para: Manage lookup of vectors of auxiliary data.
